trending_stories.title: Sekiro: No Defeat | Official Trailer | Crunchyroll
trending_stories.summary_en: The official trailer for Sekiro: No Defeat, a new game, is coming exclusively to Crunchyroll, set in a fractured Japan during the Sengoku period with a new threat emerging in Ashina.
trending_stories.description:
Sekiro: No Defeat is coming exclusively to Crunchyroll!

The time is Sengoku.

Japan is fractured into many independent nations entangled in ceaseless war. At the center lies Ashina, a land of sacred earth and ancient mystery. Two decades after Sword Saint Isshin Ashina reclaimed the region in a brutal coup, a new threat emerges from within: The Interior Ministry. Desperate to protect his homeland, Isshin‚Äôs grandson Genichiro turns to forbidden powers. The only hope lies in a kidnapped boy ‚Äî the Divine Heir ‚Äî and his silent protector: a loyal shinobi known only as Sekiro.

This is the story of a lord and his retainer ‚Äî and their quest to restore balance to a nation on the edge.

Crunchyroll brings you the latest clips, openings, full episodes, and more from your favorite anime!

trending_stories.summary_en: Game Science reveals the official trailer for Black Myth: Zhong Kui, an action RPG inspired by Chinese mythology, where players will embark on a journey to uncover the truth and face challenges in a mystical world.
trending_stories.description:
Check out the Reveal Trailer for Black Myth: Zhong Kui, an action souls-like RPG developed by Game Science. Players will continue the story of the Destined One in a Chinese mythology-inspired environment to overcome challenges, dispatch enemies along the way, and bring the truth to light. Experience new mystical happenings in the world of Black Myth: Zhong Kui, coming soon.
